    "GPT, while generating content, struggles with accuracy in quotes, factual errors, and lacks the depth and authenticity exhibited by the student's essay.",
    "These factors significantly impacted the overall authorial presence and effectiveness of the generated text.",
    "This study delved into the comparison between AI-generated text and human-authored text, specifically examining concepts of authorship and voice.",
